{"tid":1412637,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【唔好放火】農曆七月　戰線燒衣路祭死諫義士","createTime":"2019-08-05T07:20:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T03:35:41.000Z","uid":117451,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f087267dca8a51b3cd7f1b93d43dc73c3f7b9501","tid":1412637,"uid":117451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:20:38.000Z","msg":"發夢見到好多手足開始放火起防線<br />\n放火係犯法㗎！<br />\n<br />\n《空氣污染管制(露天焚燒)規例》<br />\n明文禁止多項露天焚燒活動<br />\n但<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">為祭祀用途而燃燒香蠋冥鏹</span></span></strong>則<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不受規例管制</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n依家踏入咗農曆7月<br />\n我哋唔可以忘記為我哋犧牲嘅義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n放火嘅手足可以考慮停止犯法<br />\n改燒紙紮公仔，仲大火啲，又輕<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一齊去十八區燒衣路祭死諫義士！！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n不如千萬唔好阻住條街！唔好呀！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1CrCJLN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1CrCJLN.jpg&h=69d23b5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「我拜神姐！」<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rmzs52Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frmzs52Y.png&h=073465ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲可以<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">去警署附近燒</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">路祭義警徐步高</span></strong></span><br />\n但唔好去北角警署呀！！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: brown;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">北角警署就喺香港殯儀館隔離！</span></span></strong><br />\n如果<strong><span style=\"color: brown;\">啲燒唔小心飄到入警署</span></strong>就唔好啦！<br />\n<br />\nWIKI：<br />\n「現代劣質金紙燃燒後會釋出很多有害物質<br />\n就算在戶外通風處燒金紙也很容易造成嚴重公害<br />\n危害不亞於二手菸害」<br />\n<br />\n放火嘅發夢手足，一齊買香燭冥鏹！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aa375a587f351038a099f3b60281a0b79cb163b","tid":1412637,"uid":117451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:28:19.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"07427e53a0e1c604e753f37558b713e34b68a75c","tid":1412637,"uid":117451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T09:15:24.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"e6e87856627cc98f89b547f096390b9e1ac8204f","tid":1412637,"uid":278791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T11:41:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7384da1773a83acf67a09488e406b46a9e1315be","tid":1412637,"uid":117451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:43:19.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"c79c7e06410455d9a92ec603d27059026722a113","tid":1412637,"uid":117451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:35:41.000Z","msg":"push!!"}]}